# bitmap-index-to-filter-scan

## Description

Migrated to a declarative `.rra` rule (RFC 0090 Phase 2).

## Rewrite

lhs: (bitmap-index-scan ?table auto ?pred)
rhs: (filter ?pred (scan ?table))
